Write a CRT Script for the following test case -
Test Case for Update AccountTrigger logic:
Objective: To validate that the AccountTrigger logic includes validation for the region field.
Steps:
Create a new Account record without selecting a region.
Save the record and verify that an error message is displayed, indicating that the region field is required.
Update the Account record by selecting a valid region.
Save the record and ensure that it is successfully saved without any errors.
